2/ How did the depeg happen?

$USDC is a fully reserved-backed stablecoin, meaning every $USDC is backed by actual cash and short-dated United States treasuries.

However, it can depeg from its pegged value due to market conditions, liquidity issues, or regulatory changes. https://t.co/wBsFECPnkO
